import React from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' function ResetPasswordScreen() { return (
Follow this instruction carefully.

1. First go to the below link and submit your email.

2. Check your email for password reset token (it will show you like this /api/users/password_reset/?token=d9aadce89fccd946a5b9d59cb34fcca4a0)

3. Copy and paste the token you get from your email and set a new password from there

4. After submitting the form if the status say okay then you have updated your password successfully.

5. Now try to login from here. Sign In

) } export default ResetPasswordScreen
